<plot>Five stories of service and sacrifice, all from a small area of rural Illinois. A marine survives the siege at Khe Sahn, a young man receives the Medal of Honor for his actions in the delta, an army nurse deals with the casualties of war, a young soldier is caught in one of the worst ambushes of the war, and a local woman corresponds with thousands of GI's.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?017217</url></doc>
